OL,3,CResidents left 'shaken' after petrol
OL,4,Cbomb thrown at van which ignited
OL,5,Cgardens
OL,7,FTwo men have been jailed after a
OL,8,Fvehicle was petrol bombed in Portslade
OL,9,Fin East Sussex.
OL,11,FThe petrol bombs were thrown at a van
OL,12,Foutside an address in Graham Avenue in
OL,13,FMile Oak just before 11pm on 19 June
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,16,FOfficers say a petrol bomb had also
OL,17,Fset fire to shrubbery outside of the
OL,18,Faddress which then spread to the front
OL,19,Fgardens of neighbouring houses.
