OL,7,FAshley Khan, 31, of Rodmell Avenue in
OL,8,FSaltdean and his brother Nathan
OL,9,FThomas, 33, of no fixed address, were
OL,10,Fsentenced to a total of nine and a
OL,11,Fhalf years in prison after being found
OL,12,Fguilty of conspiracy to commit arson
OL,13,Fand possession with intent to supply
OL,14,Fcocaine.
OL,16,FKhan was also found guilty of
OL,17,Fpossession of cannabis.
