OL,7,F"The impact of this crime on the
OL,8,Fvictims and the local community has
OL,9,Fbeen significant, with residents of
OL,10,Fthe usually quiet street shaken by the
OL,11,Fbrazen acts committed by Khan and
OL,12,FThomas.J"We want to express our
OL,13,Fgratitude to the community for their
OL,14,Fsupport and assistance during our
OL,15,Finvestigation.J"The eyewitness
OL,16,Faccounts provided were instrumental in
OL,17,Fhelping us narrow our search and bring
OL,18,Fthose responsible to justice."
